Entries.default: As you approach, the fish vendor flashes you a broad, cheery grin. He beckons you over with a wave of his hand and directs your attention to his latest delivery.
"You look hungry, ekera. Let me fix that for you."
"All the wonders of the sea and more besides!" He directs you to a display selling the day's catch.
"Hagfish, fresh and at a fair price!"
"Looking to spice things up in the bedroom? Try oysters and fire kelp!"
"My shop will be open in the morning."
